      <title>docker常用容器</title>
      <link href="/2022/01/27/docker%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8/"/>
      <url>/2022/01/27/docker%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="phpmyadmin"><a href="#phpmyadmin" class="headerlink" title="phpmyadmin"></a>phpmyadmin</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d \</span><br><span class="line">  --name=phpmyadmin \</span><br><span class="line">  -e PUID=1000 \</span><br><span class="line">  -e PGID=1000 \</span><br><span class="line">  -e TZ=Asia/Shanghai \</span><br><span class="line">  -p 81:80 \</span><br><span class="line">  -v /etc/docker/phpmyadmin/config:/config \</span><br><span class="line">  --restart unless-stopped \</span><br><span class="line">  -e PMA_ARBITRARY=1 \</span><br><span class="line">  --net=mynet \</span><br><span class="line">  linuxserver/phpmyadmin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span><h3 id="Potainer-ce"><a href="#Potainer-ce" class="headerlink" title="Potainer-ce"></a>Potainer-ce</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d \</span><br><span class="line">  --restart=always \</span><br><span class="line">  --name=&quot;portainer-ce&quot; \</span><br><span class="line">  -p 9000:9000 \</span><br><span class="line">  -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \</span><br><span class="line">  -v /etc/docker/portainer-ce/data:/data \</span><br><span class="line">  6053537/portainer-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Nps内网穿透服务端"><a href="#Nps内网穿透服务端" class="headerlink" title="Nps内网穿透服务端"></a>Nps内网穿透服务端</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d \</span><br><span class="line">--restart=always \</span><br><span class="line">--name=nps \</span><br><span class="line">-v /etc/docker/nps/conf:/nps/conf \</span><br><span class="line">taygetus/nps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载conf文件夹并上传到服务器。<a href="https://github.com/ehang-io/nps">https://github.com/ehang-io/nps</a></p><h3 id="Couchdb"><a href="#Couchdb" class="headerlink" title="Couchdb"></a>Couchdb</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d \</span><br><span class="line">--name couchdb \</span><br><span class="line">-e COUCHDB_USER=admin \</span><br><span class="line">-e COUCHDB_PASSWORD=a00000000 \</span><br><span class="line">--restart=always \</span><br><span class="line">-v /etc/docker/couchdb:/opt/couchdb/etc/local.d \</span><br><span class="line">-p 5984:5984 \</span><br><span class="line">couchdb:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
